name: Other policy provisions
text: §431:10A-111  Other policy provisions.  No policy provision which is not subject to section 431:10A-105 or section 431:10A-106 shall make a policy, or any portion of the policy, less favorable in any respect to the insured or the beneficiary than the provisions which are subject to this part. [L 1987, c 347, pt of §2]
